.Dd November 14, 2001
.Dt ABS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm abs
.Nd integer absolute value function
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libc
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In stdlib.h
.Ft int
.Fn abs "int j"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn abs
function
computes
the absolute value of the integer
.Fa j .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The
.Fn abs
function
returns
the absolute value.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr cabs 3 ,
.Xr fabs 3 ,
.Xr floor 3 ,
.Xr hypot 3 ,
.Xr imaxabs 3 ,
.Xr labs 3 ,
.Xr llabs 3 ,
.Xr math 3
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Fn abs
function conforms to
.St -isoC-99 .
.Sh BUGS
The absolute value of the most negative integer remains negative.
